{"id":146037,"type":1,"name":"Kanon 文庫版","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/7c/22/146037_E4euS.jpg","summary":"両親の仕事の都合で、祐一は北国の街へと引っ越すことになった。転勤族の父親のせいもあって、転校にはなれていた祐一も、この街だけは勝手が違う…。幼いころは毎年のように訪れていたはずなのに、なぜか当時の記憶が祐一には残っていない。にもかかわらず「あの街には行きたくない」という理由のない感情が、祐一の中にわきあがってくるのだ。そんな街で、親戚の家に居候することになった祐一は、7年ぶりにいとこの少女と再会し、新たな生活を始めるが…。","info":"<li><span>册数: </span>6</li><li><span>作者: </span><a href=\"/person/15561\">清水マリコ</a></li><li><span>插图: </span><a href=\"/person/2402\">樋上いたる</a>、ZEN</li><li><span>出版社: </span><a href=\"/person/2401\">Visual Art's</a></li><li><span>原作: </span><a href=\"/person/47\">Key</a></li>","collection":{"wish":2,"collect":2,"doing":1,"on_hold":1},"tags":[{"name":"不确定","count":1},{"name":"小说系列","count":1},{"name":"轻小说","count":1}],"staff":[{"id":15561,"image":"","name":"清水マリコ","desc":"作者"},{"id":2402,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/c5/57/2402_prsn_rcn3T.jpg","name":"樋上至","desc":"插图"},{"id":2401,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/5a/4a/2401_prsn_8MG8P.jpg","name":"Visual Art's","desc":"出版社"},{"id":47,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/da/92/47_prsn_I3f0W.jpg","name":"Key","desc":"原作"}],"relations":[{"id":142,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/a8/ba/142_llJLp.jpg","title":"Kanon","type":"游戏","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/142"}],"comic":[{"id":146039,"name":"Kanon 雪の少女 (1)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/d0/98/146039_jp.jpg"},{"id":146040,"name":"Kanon 笑顔の向こう側 (2)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/db/84/146040_jp.jpg"},{"id":146042,"name":"Kanon 少女の檻 (3)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/96/32/146042_jp.jpg"},{"id":146038,"name":"Kanon the fox and the grapes (4)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/80/a9/146038_jp.jpg"},{"id":146044,"name":"Kanon 日溜まりの街 (5)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/df/2e/146044_jp.jpg"},{"id":146041,"name":"Kanon 彼女たちの見解 (6)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/80/5c/146041_jp.jpg"}]}